  <LINE>The following are also exemptions from the succes-</LINE>
  <LINE>sion duty : —</LINE>
  <LINE>1. Successions from the same predecessor, passing</LINE>
  <LINE>on any death, not amounting in principal value to</LINE>
  <LINE>£100 (§ 18). 2. Any succession of less value</LINE>
  <LINE>than £20 in the whole (ib.~). 3. Legacies and</LINE>
  <LINE>personal property charged with legacy duty iu</LINE>
  <LINE>respect of the same acquisition (ib.).</LINE>
